# Vidya Kendra — TGPSC + SSC Study Desk

A free study companion for Telangana (TGPSC Group 1/2/3) and Central (SSC CGL/CHSL) government exams. Built with React + Vite.

Includes: full syllabus for all 4 tracks, illustrated notes for all 12 subjects, practice quizzes, past-paper guidance, a current-affairs system, a daily study plan, and a progress tracker (saved in your browser).

> Honest note: this is a genuine study tool, **not a guarantee of selection**. Clearing these exams needs months of consistent effort.

---

## Deploy to Vercel (easiest — no coding)

**Option A — drag & drop (fastest)**
1. Run the build locally: `npm install` then `npm run build`. This creates a `dist/` folder.
2. Go to https://vercel.com → sign up (free) → **Add New → Project → Deploy** → drag the whole project folder in.
3. Vercel auto-detects Vite. Click **Deploy**. Done — you get a public link.

**Option B — from GitHub (recommended for updates)**
1. Create a new repo on GitHub and upload all these files.
2. On Vercel: **Add New → Project → Import** your repo.
3. Framework preset: **Vite** (auto-detected). Build command `npm run build`, output `dist`.
4. Click **Deploy**. Every future push auto-updates the live site.

That's it. The site is 100% static — no API keys, no cost, no risk.

