## Run locally
```bash
npm install
npm run dev      # open the printed localhost URL
npm run build    # production build into dist/
npm run preview  # preview the production build
```

## 100% free — no API keys, no billing, ever

This app has no paid services and no API keys. It's fully static: everything runs in the browser and costs you nothing to host or share. The "Study Builder" tab is a free launcher into the built-in notes and quizzes — there is no AI generation and nothing that can bill you.

If you ever want live AI generation later, it would need a paid API and a secure backend — ask then, and weigh the cost. For now, this is genuinely free forever.

